{"kanda":6,"sarga":24,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"सावीरसमितीराज्ञाविरराजव्यवस्थिता ।शशिनाशुभनक्षत्रापौर्णमासीवशारदी","trans":"The army of Vanaras settled that way by Rama's command shone like the autumnal full moon with auspicious stars.","words":[{"d":"व्यवस्थिता","m":"settled"},{"d":"सा","m":"that"},{"d":"वीरसमितिः","m":"army of Vanaras"},{"d":"राज्ञा","m":"by the king (Rama)"},{"d":"शुभनक्षत्रा","m":"with auspicious stars"},{"d":"शारदी","m":"autumn"},{"d":"पौर्णमासी","m":"full moon"},{"d":"शशिनाइव","m":"like the moon"},{"d":"विरराज","m":"shone."}]},{"v":2,"dev":"प्रचचालचवेगेनत्रस्ताचैववसुन्धरा ।पीड्यमानाबलौघेनतेनसागरवर्चसा","trans":"The frightened army (of Vanaras) that was like a tormented ocean started moving swiftly, shaking like the earth.","words":[{"d":"सागरवर्चसा","m":"like the ocean"},{"d":"तेन","m":"by that"},{"d":"बलौघेन","m":"the army"},{"d":"पीड्यमाना","m":"tormented by"},{"d":"वसुन्धरा","m":"the earth"},{"d":"वेगेन","m":"swift movement"},{"d":"त्रस्ता","m":"frightened"},{"d":"प्रचचाल","m":"started shaking."}]},{"v":3,"dev":"ततश्शुश्रुवुराक्रुष्टंलङ्कायांकाननौकसः ।भेरीमृदङ्गसङ्घुष्टंतुमुलंरोमहर्षणम्","trans":"There upon having settled down, the army hordes heard from Lanka terrific and tumultuous noise of drums and percussion instruments that caused horripilation.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"there upon"},{"d":"काननौकसः","m":"army having settled"},{"d":"लङ्कायां","m":"from Lanka"},{"d":"आक्रुष्टम्","m":"terrific"},{"d":"तुमुलम्","m":"tumultuous"},{"d":"रेमहर्षणम्","m":"that which causes horripilation"},{"d":"भेरीमृदङ्गसङ्घुष्टम्","m":"drums and percussion instruments"},{"d":"शुश्रुवुः","m":"came to hear."}]},{"v":4,"dev":"बभूवुस्तेनघोषेणसंहृष्टाहरियूथपाः ।अमृष्यमाणास्तंघोषंविनेदुर्घोषवत्तरम्","trans":"The leaders of Vanara troops felt very happy at the noise from (Lanka) which they were unable to tolerate and roared louder (than that in joy).","words":[{"d":"हरियूथपाः","m":"leaders of Vanara troops"},{"d":"तेन","m":"of that (Lanka)"},{"d":"घोषेण","m":"by the loud noises"},{"d":"संहृष्टाः","m":"felt very happy"},{"d":"बभूवुः","m":"became"},{"d":"तम्","m":"that which"},{"d":"घोषम्","m":"noise"},{"d":"अमृष्यमाणाः","m":"unable to tolerate"},{"d":"घोषवत्तरम्","m":"louder than the noise"},{"d":"विनेदुः","m":"roared in joy."}]},{"v":5,"dev":"राक्षसास्तुप्लवङ्गानांशुश्रुवुश्चाऽपिगर्जितम् ।नर्दतामिवदृप्तानांमेघानामम्बरेस्वनम्","trans":"Even the Rakshasas heard the roaring of Vanaras in their pride that was bellowing like that of clouds in the sky.","words":[{"d":"राक्षसाःअपि","m":"even the Rakshasas"},{"d":"दृप्तानाम्","m":"in their pride"},{"d":"प्लवङ्गनाम्","m":"the Vanaras"},{"d":"अम्बरे","m":"in the sky"},{"d":"नर्दताम्","m":"bellowing"},{"d":"मेघानाम्","m":"clouds"},{"d":"स्वनम् इव","m":"like the sound"},{"d":"गर्जितम्","m":"roared"},{"d":"शुश्रुवुःच","m":"heard."}]},{"v":6,"dev":"दृष्टवादाशरथिर्लङ्कांचित्रध्वजपताकिनीम् ।जगाममनसासीतंदूयमानेनचेतसा","trans":"Afflicted by sorrow upon seeing the colourful flags and posts of Lanka even Rama's thoughts went about thinking of Sita.","words":[{"d":"दाशरधिः","m":"Rama the son of Dasaratha"},{"d":"चित्रध्वजपताकिनीम्","m":"adored with colourful flags and posts"},{"d":"लङ्काम्","m":"of Lanka"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"दूयमानेन","m":"afflicted by sorrow"},{"d":"चेतसा","m":"thinking"},{"d":"सीताम्","m":"of Sita"},{"d":"मनसा","m":"in his mind"},{"d":"जगाम","m":"went about."}]},{"v":7,"dev":"अत्रसामृगशाबाक्षीरावणेनोपरुध्यते ।अभिभूताग्रहेणेवलोहिताङ्गेनरोहिणी","trans":"The doveeyed Sita is obstructed by Ravana there (at Lanka) like the planet Rohini is caught by the red coloured planet (Mars).","words":[{"d":"मृगशाबाक्षी","m":"doveeyed"},{"d":"सा","m":"she"},{"d":"लोहिताङ्गेन","m":"red colour bodied planet (Mars)"},{"d":"ग्रहेणव","m":"caught by"},{"d":"अभिभूता","m":"conquered"},{"d":"रोहिणीव","m":"like Rohini"},{"d":"रावणेन","m":"by Ravana"},{"d":"अत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"उपरुध्यते","m":"obstructed."}]},{"v":8,"dev":"दीर्घमुष्णंचनिश्वस्यसमुद्वीक्ष्यचलक्ष्मणम् ।उवा